definition.value: Catalysis of the reaction -  benzyl (2R,3S)-2-methyl-3-hydroxybutanoate + NADP(+) -eq- benzyl 2-methyl-3-oxobutanoate + H(+) + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  NADP+ + 6-lactoyl-5,6,7,8-tetrahydropterin -eq- NADPH + H+ + 6-pyruvoyltetrahydropterin.
Catalysis of the reaction -  NAD(P)+ + (R)-3-(4-hydroxyphenyl)lactate -eq- NAD(P)H + H+ + 3-(4-hydroxyphenyl)pyruvate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  trans-4-hydroxycyclohexanecarboxylate + NAD(+) -eq- 4-oxocyclohexanecarboxylate + H(+) + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  diethyl (2R,3R)-2-methyl-3-hydroxysuccinate + NADP(+) -eq- diethyl 2-methyl-3-oxosuccinate + H(+) + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3alpha-hydroxyglycyrrhetinate + NADP(+) -eq- 3-oxoglycyrrhetinate + H(+) + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  NADP(+) + prostaglandin I(2) -eq- 15-dehydro-prostaglandin I(2) + H(+) + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  NAD(P)+ + (15S)-15-hydroxy-5,8,11-cis-13-trans-icosatetraenoate -eq- NAD(P)H + H+ + 15-oxo-5,8,11-cis-13-trans-icosatetraenoate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  testosterone + NAD+ -eq- androst-4-ene-3,17-dione + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  codeine + NADP(+) -eq- codeinone + H(+) + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (7S)-salutaridinol + NADP(+) -eq- H(+) + NADPH + salutaridine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  D-arabinitol + NAD(+) -eq- D-ribulose + H(+) + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  NADP+ + scytalone -eq- NADPH + H+ + 1,3,6,8-naphthalenetetrol.

Catalysis of the reaction -  (S)-carnitine + NAD(+) -eq- 3-dehydrocarnitine + H(+) + NADH.

Catalysis of the reaction -  NAD(P)+ + androsterone -eq- NAD(P)H + H+ + 5-alpha-androstane-3,17-dione. The reaction is B-specific (i.e. the pro-S hydrogen is transferred from the 4-position of reduced nicotinamide cofactor) with respect to NAD(P)+.

Catalysis of the reaction -  NAD+ + androstan-3-alpha,17-beta-diol -eq- 17-beta-hydroxyandrostan-3-one + NADH + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  NADP+ + testosterone -eq- NADPH + H+ + androst-4-ene-3,17-dione.
Catalysis of the reaction -  NAD+ + 3-carboxy-2-hydroxyadipate -eq- NADH + H+ + CO2 + 2-keto-adipate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  glycerate + CO2 + NAD(P)+ -eq- NAD(P)H + H+ + 2-hydroxy-3-oxosuccinate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3-hydroxybenzyl alcohol + NADP(+) -eq- 3-hydroxybenzaldehyde + H(+) + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (R)-2-hydroxystearate + NAD(+) -eq- 2-oxostearate + H(+) + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (S)-2-hydroxystearate + NAD(+) -eq- 2-oxostearate + H(+) + NADH.

Catalysis of the reaction -  2-methyl-3-phytyl-1,4-naphthoquinone + oxidized dithiothreitol + H2O -eq- 2,3-epoxy-2,3-dihydro-2-methyl-3-phytyl-1,4-naphthoquinone + 1,4-dithiothreitol.

Catalysis of the reaction -  O(2) + 2 sulochrin -eq- 2 (2S)-bisdechlorogeodin + 2 H(2)O.
Catalysis of the reaction -  O(2) + 2 sulochrin -eq- 2 (2R)-bisdechlorogeodin + 2 H(2)O.
